Package suncertify.app

Provides classes for the main application (server, local and remote clients) of the Customer Service Representative (CSR) Graphical User Interface (GUI) for Bodgitt and Scarper, LLC.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CSR The CSR class is the Customer Service Representative (CSR) application for Bodgitt and Scarper, LLC.
CSRGUI The CSRGUI class implements the Graphical User Interface (GUI) for the Customer Service Representative (CSR) application for Bodgitt and Scarper, LLC.
CSRGUIMouseAdapter The CSRGUIMouseAdapter class extends MouseAdapter, to support column sorting.
CSRGUIMouseMotionAdapter Class CSRGUIMouseMotionAdapter handles mouse motion events.
CSRGUISelectionListener The CSRGUISelectionListener class simply listens for list selection events, to enable or disable the Book button.
SubcontratorTableModel The SubcontractorTableModel class extends the AbstractTableModel abstract class, providing the information that is displayed in our JTable.
